{"tid":1432513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"懶理MINA生病 志效拍拖 TWICE時隔4個月回歸韓國舞臺？ JYP娛樂方面：\"預計9日拍攝MV\"","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:51:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"765a75e13cbd46fa62248224fc084fc55c68eaf2","tid":1432513,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"TWICE正準備回歸韓國舞臺。雖然時間未定，但考慮到MV的拍攝時間，這似乎是迫在眉睫的事情。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE將於9日拍攝新專輯的MV。爲了拍攝，正在邀請20代時裝模特級別的臨時演員。<br />\n<br />\n經紀公司JYP娛樂當天對spotvnews表示：&quot;將於9日拍攝MV。雖然正在準備回歸，但是具體的日程還沒有確定。計劃一旦決定就正式公佈。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n特別是此次回歸是隊長志效公開戀愛後的第一次舞臺，引起了粉絲的關心。此外，爲了恢復健康而處於休養期的MINA在這個月1號雖然入境韓國，但曾表示：&quot;與活動無關&quot;，因此在這次回歸中很有可能以8人活動。"},{"pid":"5b6c4fcc00684d305e3df84de1e5399528a95a59","tid":1432513,"uid":106471,"like":12,"dislike":9,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"MINA其係咪去左墮胎之後休養緊炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8552447ba5540a134644c97bbc18596c6f5acd99","tid":1432513,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79169f3c97fffe8fc0eb1232f8eaf7b88152c1e6","tid":1432513,"uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b6c4fcc00684d305e3df84de1e5399528a95a59","tid":1432513,"uid":106471,"like":12,"dislike":9,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"MINA其係咪去左墮胎之後休養緊炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"可能返韓國係逼佢錄埋今次音先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後先放產假"},{"pid":"5699f60876a3f7baea2c3890e1a4fc467f05396f","tid":1432513,"uid":167880,"like":16,"dislike":9,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:28:01.000Z",